<p><a name="-vi-du-1"></a></p>

<h3 id="33-v√≠-d·ª•">3.3. V√≠ d·ª•</h3>
<p><a name="-cac-ham-mot-bien"></a></p>

<h4 id="331-c√°c-h√†m-m·ªôt-bi·∫øn">3.3.1. C√°c h√†m m·ªôt bi·∫øn</h4>
<p><strong>C√°c v√≠ d·ª• v·ªÅ c√°c <em>convex functions</em> m·ªôt bi·∫øn:</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>H√†m \( y = ax + b\) l√† m·ªôt <em>h√†m l·ªìi</em> v√¨ ƒë∆∞·ªùng n·ªëi hai ƒëi·ªÉm b·∫•t k·ª≥ n·∫±m tr√™n ch√≠nh ƒë·ªì th·ªã ƒë√≥.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>H√†m \(y = e^{ax}\) v·ªõi \(a \in \mathbb{R}\) b·∫•t k·ª≥.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>H√†m \(y = x^a\) tr√™n t·∫≠p c√°c s·ªë th·ª±c d∆∞∆°ng v√† \(a \geq 1\) ho·∫∑c \(a \leq 0\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>H√†m <em>negative entropy</em> \(y = x \log x\) tr√™n t·∫≠p c√°c s·ªë th·ª±c d∆∞∆°ng.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>D∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y l√† ƒë·ªì th·ªã c·ªßa m·ªôt v√†i <em>convex functions</em>:</p>
<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
 <img src="/assets/16_convexity/convexfunctions.png" align="center" width="800" />
 <div class="thecap">H√¨nh 8. V√≠ d·ª• v·ªÅ c√°c convex functions m·ªôt bi·∫øn.</div>
</div>
<hr />

<p><strong>C√°c v√≠ d·ª• v·ªÅ c√°c <em>concave functions</em> m·ªôt bi·∫øn:</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>H√†m \(y = ax + b\) l√† m·ªôt <em>concave function</em> v√¨ \(-y\) l√† m·ªôt <em>convex function</em>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>H√†m \(y = x^a\) tr√™n t·∫≠p s·ªë d∆∞∆°ng v√† \(0 \leq a \leq 1\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>H√†m logarithm \(y = \log(x)\) tr√™n t·∫≠p c√°c s·ªë d∆∞∆°ng.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>D∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y l√† ƒë·ªì th·ªã c·ªßa m·ªôt v√†i <em>concave functions</em>:</p>
<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
 <img src="/assets/16_convexity/concavefunctions.png" align="center" width="800" />
 <div class="thecap">H√¨nh 9. V√≠ d·ª• v·ªÅ c√°c concave functions m·ªôt bi·∫øn.</div>
