<p><a name="-affine-functions"></a></p>

<h4 id="333-affine-functions">3.3.3. Affine functions</h4>
<p>C√°c h√†m s·ªë d·∫°ng \(f(\mathbf{x}) = \mathbf{a}^T\mathbf{x} + b \) v·ª´a l√† convex, v·ª´a l√† concave.</p>

<p>Khi bi·∫øn l√† m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{X}\), c√°c h√†m affine ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a c√≥ d·∫°ng:
\[
f(\mathbf{X}) = \text{trace}(\mathbf{A}^T\mathbf{X}) + b
\]
trong ƒë√≥ \(\text{trace}\) l√† h√†m s·ªë t√≠nh t·ªïng c√°c gi√° tr·ªã tr√™n ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o c·ªßa m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n vu√¥ng, \(\mathbf{A}\) l√† m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n c√≥ c√πng chi·ªÅu v·ªõi \(\mathbf{X}\) (ƒë·ªÉ ƒë·∫£m b·∫£o ph√©p nh√¢n ma tr·∫≠n th·ª±c hi·ªán ƒë∆∞·ª£c v√† k·∫øt qu·∫£ l√† m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n vu√¥ng).</p>

<p><a name="-quadratic-forms"></a></p>

<h4 id="333-quadratic-forms">3.3.3. Quadratic forms</h4>
<p>H√†m b·∫≠c hai m·ªôt bi·∫øn c√≥ d·∫°ng \(f(x) = a x^2 + bx + c\) l√† convex n·∫øu \(a &gt; 0\), l√† concave n·∫øu \(a &lt; 0\).</p>

<p>V·ªõi bi·∫øn l√† m·ªôt vector \(\mathbf{x} = [x_1, x_2, \dots, x_n]\), m·ªôt quadratic form l√† m·ªôt h√†m s·ªë c√≥ d·∫°ng:
\[
f(\mathbf{x}) = \mathbf{x}^T\mathbf{A}\mathbf{x} + \mathbf{b}^T\mathbf{x} + c
\]
V·ªõi \(\mathbf{A}\) th∆∞·ªùng l√† m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n ƒë·ªëi x·ª©ng, t·ª©c \(a_{ij} = a_{ji}, \forall i, j\), c√≥ s·ªë h√†ng b·∫±ng s·ªë ph·∫©n t·ª≠ c·ªßa \(\mathbf{x}\), \(\mathbf{b}\) l√† m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n b·∫•t k·ª≥ c√πng chi·ªÅu v·ªõi \(\mathbf{x}\) v√† \(c\) l√† m·ªôt h·∫±ng s·ªë b·∫•t k·ª≥.</p>

<p>N·∫øu \(\mathbf{A}\) l√† m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n (n·ª≠a) x√°c ƒë·ªãnh d∆∞∆°ng th√¨ \(f(\mathbf{x})\) l√† m·ªôt <em>convex function</em>.</p>

<p>N·∫øu \(\mathbf{A}\) l√† m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n (n·ª≠a) x√°c ƒë·ªãnh √¢m, t·ª©c \(\mathbf{x}^T\mathbf{A}\mathbf{x} \leq 0, \forall \mathbf{x}\), th√¨ \(f(\mathbf{x})\) l√† m·ªôt <em>concave function</em>.</p>

<p><em>C√°c b·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ t√¨m ƒë·ªçc v·ªÅ ma tr·∫≠n x√°c ƒë·ªãnh d∆∞∆°ng v√† c√°c t√≠nh ch·∫•t c·ªßa n√≥ trong s√°ch ƒê·∫°i s·ªë tuy·∫øn t√≠nh b·∫•t k·ª≥. N·∫øu b·∫°n g·∫∑p nhi·ªÅu kh√≥ khƒÉn trong ph·∫ßn n√†y, h√£y ƒë·ªçc l·∫°i ki·∫øn th·ª©c v·ªÅ ƒê·∫°i s·ªë tuy·∫øn t√≠nh, r·∫•t r·∫•t quan tr·ªçng trong T·ªëi ∆Øu v√† Machine Learning.</em></p>

<p><a href="/2016/12/28/linearregression/#ham-mat-mat">H√†m m·∫•t m√°t trong Linear Regression</a> c√≥ d·∫°ng:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\mathcal{L}(\mathbf{w}) &amp;=&amp; \frac{1}{2} ||\mathbf{y} - \mathbf{X}\mathbf{w}||_2^2 = \frac{1}{2} (\mathbf{y} - \mathbf{X}\mathbf{w})^T(\mathbf{y} - \mathbf{X}\mathbf{w})  \<br />
&amp;=&amp; \frac{1}{2} \mathbf{w}^T\mathbf{X}^T\mathbf{Xw} - \mathbf{y}^T\mathbf{Xw} + \frac{1}{2}\mathbf{y}^T\mathbf{y}
\end{eqnarray}
\]
v√¨ \(\mathbf{X}^T\mathbf{X}\) l√† m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n x√°c ƒë·ªãnh d∆∞∆°ng, h√†m m·∫•t m√°t c·ªßa Linear Regression ch√≠nh l√† m·ªôt convex function.</p>

<p><a name="-norms"></a></p>

<h4 id="334-norms">3.3.4. Norms</h4>
<p>V√¢ng, l·∫°i l√† norms. M·ªôt h√†m s·ªë b·∫•t k·ª≥ th·ªèa m√£n <a href="/math/#-norms-chuan">ba ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán c·ªßa norm</a> ƒë·ªÅu l√† m·ªôt <em>convex function</em>. B·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c√≥ th·ªÉ ch·ª©ng minh ƒëi·ªÅu n√†y b·∫±ng ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a.</p>

<p>D∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y l√† hai v√≠ d·ª• v·ªÅ norm 1 (tr√°i) v√† norm 2 (ph·∫£i) v·ªõi s·ªë chi·ªÅu l√† 2 (chi·ªÅu th·ª© ba trong h√¨nh d∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y l√† gi√° tr·ªã c·ªßa h√†m s·ªë).</p>
